item.title: About
item.description: My name is Yeabsira T. Bekele. I am an aspiring data scientist who is and will forever be obsessed with using data science tools to unravel the mysteries hunting the fields of Biology and Physics, and hope to unravel the grander mysteries of our universe. To that end, I am eagerly in pursuit of trading sleep with persistent study sessions in hopes of putting forth significant contributions to the collective effort.
